        "solutionCode": "def is_in_range(number):\n    if number >= 10 and number <= 20:\n        return True\n    return False\n\nimport ast\n\ndef _parse_arg(raw):\n    try:\n        return ast.literal_eval(raw)\n    except Exception:\n        return raw\n\n_inputs = []\ntry:\n    while True:\n        _inputs.append(input())\nexcept EOFError:\n    pass\nnumber = _parse_arg(_inputs[0]) if len(_inputs) > 0 else \"\"\n\nprint(is_in_range(number))"
